{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_016bGyade6SqgMkz8J4LHMw4","type":"tool_result","content":"     1→# Implementation History — 300-referral-system\n     2→\n     3→Iteration log for the autonomous spec loop. Each entry records what was\n     4→attempted and whether it succeeded. The agent reads this file at the start\n     5→of every iteration to understand prior context.\n     6→\n     7→---\n     8→\n     9→## Iteration 1 — 2026-03-24T21:27:27Z — OK\n    10→\n    11→**Item**: [backend] Database migration `011_referral.sql`\n    12→**Status**: Done\n    13→**Changes**:\n    14→- Created `services/backend/migrations/011_referral.sql` with all 5 referral tables:\n    15→  - `referral_codes` — one code per wallet (UNIQUE on wallet + code)\n    16→  - `referral_links` — immutable referrer binding (UNIQUE on referee_wallet)\n    17→  - `referral_earnings` — per-game earnings with idempotency guard (UNIQUE on referee_wallet + round_id)\n    18→  - `referral_claims` — async payout tracking with status CHECK constraint (pending/processing/completed/failed)\n    19→  - `referral_kol_rates` — KOL custom rates (wallet PK)\n    20→- Indexes: referrer/referee wallet lookups on earnings, round_id, claims by wallet+date, partial index on pending/processing claims, referrer_wallet on links\n    21→- Follows existing migration patterns (IF NOT EXISTS, TIMESTAMPTZ, BIGINT for lamports, no foreign keys)\n    22→**Verification**: `pnpm lint` passed (18/18 tasks)\n    23→**Note**: Agent falsely claimed DONE after this single item. Loop accepted it (no guard).\n    24→\n    25→## Gap Analysis — 2026-03-24T21:41:16Z\n    26→- **Result**: Gap analysis report generated\n    27→- **Report**: gap-analysis.md\n    28→- **Log**: gap-analysis.log\n    29→\n    30→## Iteration 2 — 2026-03-25T08:54:27Z — FALSE DONE (rejected retroactively)\n    31→- **Agent claimed DONE** but only the migration was complete. Checklist was refined between runs.\n    32→- **Log**: iteration-002.log\n    33→\n    34→## Iteration 3 — 2026-03-25T09:09:19Z — OK\n    35→\n    36→**Item**: [backend] DB client methods in `db.ts`: `insertReferralCode`, `getReferralCodeByWallet`, `getReferralCodeByCode`, `upsertReferralCode` for code CRUD\n    37→**Status**: Done\n    38→**Changes**:\n    39→- Added `ReferralCode` interface to type section (id, wallet, code, created_at, updated_at)\n    40→- Added 4 method signatures to `Db` interface: `insertReferralCode`, `getReferralCodeByWallet`, `getReferralCodeByCode`, `upsertReferralCode`\n    41→- Implemented all 4 methods in `createDb()`:\n    42→  - `insertReferralCode`: INSERT with RETURNING *\n    43→  - `getReferralCodeByWallet`: SELECT by wallet, returns undefined if not found\n    44→  - `getReferralCodeByCode`: SELECT by code, returns undefined if not found\n    45→  - `upsertReferralCode`: INSERT ON CONFLICT (wallet) DO UPDATE — replaces code for existing wallet\n    46→**Verification**: `pnpm lint` passed (18/18 tasks)\n    47→**Note**: Agent falsely claimed DONE after this single item. Loop accepted it (no guard).\n    48→\n    49→## Gap Analysis — 2026-03-25T09:26:04Z\n    50→- **Result**: Gap analysis report updated (post-iteration-3)\n    51→- **Report**: gap-analysis.md\n    52→- **Totals**: 15 SATISFIED, 0 DEFERRED, 75 GAP (90 total criteria)\n    53→\n    54→## Iteration 4 — 2026-03-25 — OK\n    55→\n    56→**Item**: [backend] DB client methods: `insertReferralLink`, `getReferralLinkByReferee`, referral link queries\n    57→**Status**: Done\n    58→**Changes**:\n    59→- Added `ReferralLink` interface to type section (id, referrer_wallet, referee_wallet, created_at)\n    60→- Added 3 method signatures to `Db` interface: `insertReferralLink`, `getReferralLinkByReferee`, `getReferralLinksByReferrer`\n    61→- Implemented all 3 methods in `createDb()`:\n    62→  - `insertReferralLink`: INSERT with RETURNING *\n    63→  - `getReferralLinkByReferee`: SELECT by referee_wallet, returns undefined if not found\n    64→  - `getReferralLinksByReferrer`: SELECT all links where wallet is referrer, ordered by created_at DESC\n    65→**Verification**: `pnpm lint` passed (18/18 tasks)\n    66→\n    67→## Fix — 2026-03-25 — Loop signal detection bug\n    68→- **Problem**: Signal detection (`rg` on raw stream-json log) matched tag text inside tool results (files the agent read), not just agent output. History file containing the DONE tag as prose triggered false positive.\n    69→- **Fix**: Signal detection now extracts only assistant text via `jq` before searching for tags. Also added mandatory Checklist Audit step in prompt (agent must enumerate all items before claiming done).\n    70→- **Spec update**: Referral codes changed to always be player-chosen (3-16 chars, `[a-z0-9-]`). No auto-generation.\n    71→\n    72→## Iteration 4 — 2026-03-25T10:22:52Z — FALSE DONE (signal detection bug)\n    73→- **Result**: Agent did NOT claim done (said \"29 items remain\"), but script matched DONE tag in history file tool result\n    74→- **Log**: iteration-004.log\n    75→\n    76→## Devnet E2E — 2026-03-25T10:22:57Z\n    77→- **Result**: PASS\n    78→\n    79→## Gap Analysis — 2026-03-25 (post-iteration-4)\n    80→- **Result**: Gap analysis report updated\n    81→- **Report**: gap-analysis.md\n    82→- **Totals**: 17 SATISFIED, 0 DEFERRED, 73 GAP (90 total criteria)\n    83→- **Changes vs previous**: +2 SATISFIED (link CRUD methods: `insertReferralLink`, `getReferralLinkByReferee`, `getReferralLinksByReferrer` added to db.ts; updated evidence for FR-2 criteria 2d, 2f)\n    84→- **Spec FR checkboxes**: Updated with evidence annotations\n    85→\n    86→## Gap Analysis — 2026-03-25T10:43:21Z\n    87→- **Result**: Gap analysis report generated\n    88→- **Report**: gap-analysis.md\n    89→- **Log**: gap-analysis.log\n    90→\n    91→## Iteration 5 — 2026-03-25 — OK\n    92→\n    93→**Item**: [backend] DB client methods: `insertReferralEarning`, `getPendingBalance`, `getReferralEarnings`, `getReferralStats`\n    94→**Status**: Done\n    95→**Changes**:\n    96→- Added `ReferralEarning` interface (id, referrer_wallet, referee_wallet, round_id, game_type, wager_lamports, fee_lamports, referrer_earned_lamports, referrer_rate_bps, referee_rebate_lamports, referee_rebate_rate_bps, created_at)\n    97→- Added `ReferralStats` interface (referred_count, active_count, total_volume_lamports, total_earned_lamports, pending_lamports)\n    98→- Added `normalizeReferralEarning()` helper to convert BIGINT columns to JS numbers\n    99→- Added 4 method signatures to `Db` interface + implementations in `createDb()`:\n   100→  - `insertReferralEarning(params)`: INSERT with all earning fields, RETURNING *, normalized\n   101→  - `getPendingBalance(wallet)`: SUM(referrer_earned where referrer) + SUM(referee_rebate where referee) - SUM(completed/pending/processing claims). Returns lamport string\n   102→  - `getReferralEarnings(wallet, page, limit)`: paginated SELECT by referrer_wallet, newest first, with totalPages count\n   103→  - `getReferralStats(wallet)`: single query returning referred_count, active_count (7d), total_volume, total_earned, pending_lamports\n   104→**Verification**: `pnpm lint` passed (18/18). Backend typecheck has 1 pre-existing error (HealthDeps in endpoints.test.ts) — no new errors introduced.\n   105→\n   106→## Iteration 5 — 2026-03-25T11:43:58Z — OK\n   107→- **Log**: iteration-005.log\n   108→\n   109→## Iteration 6 — 2026-03-25 — OK\n   110→\n   111→**Item**: [backend] DB client methods: `insertReferralClaim`, `getReferralClaim`, `updateClaimStatus`, `getReferrerRate(wallet)`\n   112→**Status**: Done\n   113→**Changes**:\n   114→- Added `ReferralClaim` interface (id, wallet, amount_lamports, status, tx_signature, error, requested_at, processed_at)\n   115→- Added 4 method signatures to `Db` interface + implementations in `createDb()`:\n   116→  - `insertReferralClaim(wallet, amountLamports)`: INSERT with status='pending', RETURNING